children.name: SELECT "order_shippingevent"."id", "order_shippingevent"."order_id", "order_shippingevent"."event_type_id", "order_shippingevent"."notes", "order_shippingevent"."date_created" FROM "order_shippingevent" INNER JOIN "order_shippingeventquantity" ON ("order_shippingevent"."id" = "order_shippingeventquantity"."event_id") WHERE "order_shippingeventquantity"."line_id" = 174 ORDER BY "order_shippingevent"."date_created" DESC
